Class DocumentStart

java.lang.Object
org.opensextant.giscore.events.DocumentStart
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, IGISObject, VisitableGeometry
public class DocumentStart extends Object implements IGISObject
This tags the document with the source information of what format it came from, useful for back end processors to decide on the meaning of various values.

    • addNamespace

      public boolean addNamespace(Namespace aNamespace)
      Add namespace. Verifies namespace prefix is unique in the list as required in a XML context with the XML unique attribute constraint. Duplicate prefixes are discarded and not added to the list. URIs may be duplicates in the list but its prefix must be different.
      Parameters:
      aNamespace - Namespace to add, never null
      Returns:
      true if namespace was added or if already existed in the list, otherwise false if not added because either argument was null or its prefix conflicted with one having another URI.
